For Setting up the docker environment : Follow steps below:

1.Configure yum -> cd /etc/yum.repos.d and create docker.repo by using gedit docker.repo
and enter the following data ->
[docker]
baseurl=https://download.docker.com/linux/centos/7/x86_64/stable/
gpgchech=0
Then save and exit gedit.
This will configure yum for doccker installation.

2.Install Docker application using YUM command 
yum install docker-ce --nobest


3.Start docker services
Systemctl start docker

